Your `for` loop should increment `i` by `1` each time it runs. Use the increment operator for this.

```js
assert.match(getCaloriesFromInputs.toString(), /for\s*\(\s*(let|var)\s+i\s*=\s*0\s*;\s*i\s*<\s*list\.length\s*;\s*i\s*\+\+\s*\)/g);
